Some more fun updates here...

### Separated color mode docs

I've moved the color mode docs from `/customize/color` to `/customize/color-mode` right after that page. Also exploring previous/next links in the docs to help folks navigate as they read specific pages. More on that in another PR most likely.

### New `color-mode()` mixin and `$color-mode-type` var

I've added a mixin that can return either the `data-bs-theme` selector (by default), or return a media query. This works well for light/dark control in multiple situations. If you need multiple themes, obviously stick to the `data` attribute default. But cool for folks who want automatic theming!

```scss
$color-mode-type:             data !default;

@mixin color-mode($mode: light, $type: $color-mode-type) {
  @if $type == "media-query" {
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: $mode) {
      @content;
    }
  } @else {
    [data-bs-theme="#{$mode}"] {
      @content;
    }
  }
}
```

